WEBVTT

01:38.120 --> 01:40.480
EPISODE 27

01:41.240 --> 01:44.280
You mean, you want me
to badmouth her to others?

01:44.880 --> 01:47.280
No. That's not what we meant.

01:47.560 --> 01:50.080
We just think it's very unfair

01:50.480 --> 01:51.880
when you see the villain gloating.

01:54.120 --> 01:57.960
Well, this requires a long strategy.
Let me think as I eat.

02:04.800 --> 02:05.760
Er-xi!

02:07.160 --> 02:08.000
Wei-wei!

02:10.039 --> 02:13.200
- Why is she--
- Fancy running into you here!

02:13.280 --> 02:16.120
I hear this place has yummy chicken wings.

02:16.840 --> 02:18.000
What are you doing here?

02:20.400 --> 02:21.880
Let me introduce you.

02:23.080 --> 02:26.040
This is the campus belle, Yi-ran Meng.

02:26.120 --> 02:27.240
I think you know her.

02:27.720 --> 02:29.520
This is her roommate, Nana.

02:29.600 --> 02:33.160
We're both interns at Zhenyi Tech.
We're very close.

02:33.240 --> 02:34.760
They're treating me to dinner!

02:36.760 --> 02:39.160
Er-xi has a big appetite.
You're treating her to dinner?

02:42.040 --> 02:43.400
You're so nice.

02:44.520 --> 02:47.560
- Aren't you heartbroken?
- I am.

02:50.480 --> 02:52.520
My Beckham!

02:52.800 --> 02:56.840
Why did you marry that wench, Victoria?

02:56.920 --> 02:58.800
And you had a bunch of kids!

02:58.880 --> 03:00.360
My heart aches so!

03:02.880 --> 03:04.160
Being heartbroken is painful.

03:05.120 --> 03:07.560
Poor kid. It's been years.

03:07.640 --> 03:09.520
She hasn't recovered from it.

03:10.680 --> 03:11.680
You...

03:13.080 --> 03:15.560
I'm telling you,
Wei-wei is my good friend.

03:15.920 --> 03:17.400
Eat some, too, Wei-wei.

03:18.280 --> 03:20.560
It's okay. I'll take a rain check.

03:20.640 --> 03:24.280
After all, not everyone's interested
in other people's food.

03:28.360 --> 03:29.360
I need to go.

03:30.320 --> 03:31.320
Yi-ran!

03:31.400 --> 03:33.240
Server! Give them the bill!

03:40.720 --> 03:43.200
Yi-ran. Let me explain, Yi-ran!

03:43.280 --> 03:45.640
- I didn't know they were still friends.
- Leave me alone.

03:45.840 --> 03:48.840
No, Yi-ran! Listen to me, Yi-ran!

03:50.680 --> 03:52.920
Wait! Yi-ran,
I didn't know they were still friends.

03:53.000 --> 03:53.920
Drive.

04:01.200 --> 04:03.720
Stop eating. I'll take you somewhere else.

04:04.080 --> 04:05.480
There's still so much food.

04:06.000 --> 04:06.960
Show some backbone!

04:07.040 --> 04:09.120
I just said, we don't eat others' food.
Come on!

04:11.360 --> 04:14.160
- Let me eat some more.
- Come on, let's go!

04:19.079 --> 04:21.600
I shouldn't have ordered so much food.

04:21.680 --> 04:24.000
It felt good to waste their money,

04:24.080 --> 04:29.520
but it's still a shame to squander
so much yummy food.

04:30.400 --> 04:33.680
Why? Should we take more food away?

04:46.600 --> 04:47.520
A-shuang?

04:49.120 --> 04:50.120
What is it?

04:51.480 --> 04:52.920
I saw someone I know.

04:53.760 --> 04:55.840
Shouldn't he be working overtime
at the office?

04:56.040 --> 04:57.440
What's he doing here?

05:15.160 --> 05:19.560
Mister, can we go back
and pick up the girl I was with?

05:20.200 --> 05:21.920
Why didn't she get in earlier?

05:35.240 --> 05:36.080
Stop the car.

05:41.600 --> 05:43.240
So what if you're stinkng rich?

05:43.320 --> 05:44.680
Must everyone wait on you?

05:44.760 --> 05:46.800
It serves you right,
Nai Xiao doesn't like you.

05:46.880 --> 05:49.640
If you got everything you wanted,
that'd be so unfair.

05:50.080 --> 05:52.360
I hope no one will ever truly love you.

05:52.440 --> 05:53.640
That'd really make my day.

05:53.720 --> 05:55.120
So what if you're pretty?

05:55.200 --> 05:58.280
You're still stupid
and get bossed around by me.

05:59.840 --> 06:01.360
Are we still picking her up?

06:01.840 --> 06:02.800
Just drive.

06:22.960 --> 06:24.000
Well?

06:24.400 --> 06:27.520
The number's the same as this morning.
Still at 1.1 GB.

06:39.840 --> 06:41.640
ZHIYI TECH

06:42.280 --> 06:43.400
Here's the document.

06:44.040 --> 06:45.880
- Thanks.
- Do you need anything else?

06:45.960 --> 06:47.720
- No.
- Okay.

06:56.240 --> 06:58.560
Come get lunch! Thanks.

07:01.080 --> 07:02.480
These are for today.

07:02.560 --> 07:05.760
And this is last week's invoice.
Take a look.

07:07.280 --> 07:10.360
Um... What's with this company?

07:10.440 --> 07:12.760
You don't have a normal reception desk?

07:12.840 --> 07:13.960
Every time I come,

07:14.400 --> 07:15.960
he's always acting weird here.

07:16.240 --> 07:18.880
If I weren't so brave,
I'd be scared to deliver to you.

07:18.960 --> 07:20.960
Are you a legit establishment?

07:23.160 --> 07:26.640
We're a normal gaming company.
Absolutely legit.

07:27.640 --> 07:29.560
Well then, he...

07:31.960 --> 07:33.240
What you don't know is

07:33.320 --> 07:38.320
a lot of spiritual energy gathers here,
so it's easier to find inspiration.

07:39.160 --> 07:42.480
When our programmers get coder's block,

07:42.720 --> 07:44.000
this is where they come.

07:44.680 --> 07:46.120
Sounds like mystical high tech.

07:46.680 --> 07:49.760
But he looks like
he hasn't washed his hair in days.

07:49.960 --> 07:52.680
Is this hairdo
also meant to find inspiration?

07:52.920 --> 07:57.800
Look, with his hair spiked up,
it's easier to receive inspiration.

07:58.560 --> 08:00.200
It kind of works like an antenna.

08:00.840 --> 08:03.320
That does make some sense.

08:03.400 --> 08:05.520
- The invoice is fine. I'll settle it.
- Okay.

08:10.120 --> 08:12.920
- Come on, let's eat.
- Got it.

08:13.000 --> 08:15.240
Deliver every day this week, too?

08:16.600 --> 08:18.760
Make lunch on the 31 the last delivery.

08:18.840 --> 08:21.160
- I'll call you, if we need more.
- Okay.

08:44.640 --> 08:49.600
Mr. Qiu, are they stuck
on a problem or something?

08:49.680 --> 08:50.800
Why don't they come out to eat?

08:51.800 --> 08:53.840
That's right, we did a test this morning.

08:53.920 --> 08:55.640
Optimization didn't reach
the expected result.

09:01.240 --> 09:04.720
Ms. Wei-wei, we're so pressed for time,

09:05.120 --> 09:06.720
it's only normal that
the quality of his work

09:06.800 --> 09:08.680
would suffer a little, right?

09:09.320 --> 09:11.720
Nai is too insistent on perfection.

09:11.920 --> 09:13.760
Now he's teamed up with K.O.,

09:14.080 --> 09:15.920
also a perfectionist

09:16.520 --> 09:18.000
with a penchant for reaching goals.

09:18.200 --> 09:21.600
The combination of these two
is too much for me.

09:22.560 --> 09:23.520
Let's eat.

09:38.000 --> 09:39.960
Nai's been holed up in there for two days?

09:40.040 --> 09:41.200
He hasn't slept?

09:43.360 --> 09:45.720
They were up, when I left last night.

09:45.800 --> 09:48.600
They were already working,
when I got here in the morning.

09:48.920 --> 09:51.440
But Lord slept for 30 minutes at noon.

09:51.520 --> 09:54.240
If they keep this up,
won't their bodies crash?

09:54.440 --> 09:56.320
Why should you worry about that?

09:56.520 --> 09:57.720
I finally get it now.

09:58.000 --> 10:00.840
The difference between me and them
isn't up here.

10:00.920 --> 10:02.080
It's about energy and stamina.

10:02.440 --> 10:03.760
Look at those two deviants.

10:04.000 --> 10:06.200
They sleep three hours a day,
yet are still energetic.

10:06.280 --> 10:07.440
They're inhuman!

10:08.280 --> 10:09.520
But it's already the 30th.

10:09.600 --> 10:11.240
We're flying to Shanghai tomorrow night.

10:11.320 --> 10:13.960
They're still stuck. Will we make it?

10:14.240 --> 10:15.600
Forget those two.

10:15.960 --> 10:18.320
I've seen the optimization results.

10:18.400 --> 10:20.800
It's pretty good, albeit not yet ideal.

10:21.720 --> 10:23.600
So, these two are deviants.

10:24.120 --> 10:26.400
We can't help it that they're masochists.

10:26.840 --> 10:29.920
Even if we present this version right now,
we won't lose.

10:31.720 --> 10:33.480
Should we ask them to come out and eat?

10:34.400 --> 10:36.840
No, Ms. Wei-wei. Leave the food here.

10:36.920 --> 10:38.640
They'll come out when they're hungry.

11:58.960 --> 12:01.520
- You're out!
- Yes.

12:04.200 --> 12:05.680
Let me heat it up. It's gone cold.

12:06.080 --> 12:07.680
It's okay. I'm done eating.

12:10.840 --> 12:12.880
Come on, I'll take you somewhere.

12:13.480 --> 12:15.560
- Where?
- Flower market.

12:16.800 --> 12:19.200
- It's a long way. Why there?
- You'll find out soon.

12:22.800 --> 12:23.960
Swap the two formats.

12:24.040 --> 12:26.680
- Will it be ready by tomorrow?
- I think so.

12:27.600 --> 12:29.040
Where are you off to, Nai?

12:41.040 --> 12:42.360
How come it's so empty?

12:43.560 --> 12:45.400
Wouldn't it be odd, if it were crowded?

12:46.760 --> 12:50.400
- It's Chinese Valentine's Day today.
- Chinese Valentine's Day?

12:50.840 --> 12:56.000
Yes, this place was always bustling
on Chinese Valentine's Day.

12:57.560 --> 13:00.280
I never took you out all summer.
So I wanted to bring you here.

13:01.240 --> 13:04.640
Aren't you a bit thoughtless,
waiting this long?

13:07.240 --> 13:10.480
But, Wei-wei,
you never took me here, either.

13:11.240 --> 13:13.360
- What?
- You even forgot Chinese Valentine's Day.

13:14.920 --> 13:16.600
That's very thoughtless of you.

13:18.600 --> 13:22.400
So sorry. Will my boyfriend

13:22.480 --> 13:25.320
please be the bigger person
and forgive me?

13:31.240 --> 13:33.800
I forgive you reluctantly. Never again.

13:43.120 --> 13:44.240
Why are you so quiet?

13:45.480 --> 13:47.520
I want you to rest your brains.

13:48.640 --> 13:51.040
You only slept a little yesterday.

13:51.280 --> 13:53.200
Now you're taking me out.

13:53.320 --> 13:55.080
I'd rather you use the time to sleep.

13:56.280 --> 13:57.200
I don't feel tired.

13:58.720 --> 14:01.720
You mean, I can boss you around
as much as I want?

14:03.000 --> 14:05.840
I don't think you've ever
bossed me around. You can try.

14:07.760 --> 14:09.440
I could take that as a threat.

14:10.360 --> 14:11.200
It's an invitation.

14:12.040 --> 14:14.800
It's okay, you've been so busy.

14:14.880 --> 14:16.000
I won't give you a quest.

14:18.800 --> 14:19.840
A couple's quest?

14:25.320 --> 14:27.840
Are you and K.O. stuck on something?

14:29.840 --> 14:32.680
We're still a bit off
from the expected result.

14:34.440 --> 14:37.360
Houzi Jiu told me,
your work is already excellent.

14:37.440 --> 14:38.920
You're just too insistent on perfection.

14:40.200 --> 14:43.040
I'm not saying you should give up.
It's just...

14:43.760 --> 14:45.240
Don't be so hard on yourself.

14:45.880 --> 14:48.280
Perhaps if you rest a bit
and get inspired,

14:48.360 --> 14:50.520
you'll have better results. Right?

14:53.760 --> 14:54.600
Let's go.

14:58.720 --> 15:01.360
Right now, there's probably more bustling

15:01.440 --> 15:03.240
in the game, than in real life.

15:03.320 --> 15:05.640
They're probably setting off fireworks.

15:26.960 --> 15:28.000
What's the matter?

15:30.880 --> 15:33.640
- I got it!
- Got what?

19:39.440 --> 19:41.120
We should be okay now.

19:42.400 --> 19:44.480
- It'll work for sure this time.
- Yes.

19:45.840 --> 19:47.600
The equipment pack is well made, too.

19:48.160 --> 19:49.320
- It'll be fine.
- Hey.

19:49.400 --> 19:51.640
Why does everyone look so nervous?

19:51.720 --> 19:54.680
Early this morning,
Mr. Xiao said he's nailed it.

19:54.760 --> 19:56.560
Now they're running the program.

19:56.880 --> 19:58.680
We're waiting to see the result.

20:02.520 --> 20:05.480
How late did he stay up last night?

20:28.880 --> 20:30.160
Running a normal scene,

20:30.240 --> 20:32.240
the RAM usage is about 750.

20:32.320 --> 20:33.280
It's lower than expected.

20:33.640 --> 20:35.160
Let's simulate
the Hebo flood-fighting scene.

20:48.360 --> 20:51.960
It's so smooth, I could cry.
No graphics corruption at all.

20:52.400 --> 20:53.760
It's 880 at the highest.

20:54.480 --> 20:56.280
The average is maintained at around 820.

20:56.920 --> 20:59.720
Yes! It's consistently taking up
less than 1 GB.

21:00.120 --> 21:01.520
We did it, Nai!

21:02.040 --> 21:05.080
We reduced the RAM usage by nearly half.

21:07.240 --> 21:09.440
We did it! We made it!

21:09.520 --> 21:12.040
No more overtime! I want to sleep!

21:12.120 --> 21:14.240
I want to sleep for 100 hours!

21:14.920 --> 21:16.440
- Did it work?
- Is it done?

21:16.520 --> 21:17.880
- Seriously?
- We did it!

21:17.960 --> 21:19.320
They did it?

21:19.400 --> 21:21.760
It must be, Mei is hugging everyone.

21:24.320 --> 21:26.920
Come here. Thanks for your hard work.

21:27.000 --> 21:29.560
Here, Nai! Thanks for your hard work!

21:30.600 --> 21:33.400
Nai! K.O.! This time, I have to admit,

21:33.680 --> 21:36.280
you two are slightly better than me.

21:36.360 --> 21:37.600
Yeah, right!

21:41.480 --> 21:42.960
- Here they come.
- They're out.

21:47.920 --> 21:49.720
Well? Mr. Xiao, have we made it?

21:51.600 --> 21:54.240
Everyone, despite the tight schedule,

21:54.520 --> 21:56.720
we still completed
the optimization in time.

21:57.920 --> 22:00.040
- Excellent.
- We really did it.

22:00.120 --> 22:03.080
I'm so surprised.
There's no graphics corruption?

22:03.160 --> 22:05.240
Don't worry. It's absolutely perfect.

22:05.320 --> 22:11.400
- Please reward us.
- I'll slip in there.

22:13.200 --> 22:15.880
As previously planned, this time,
I, Ban-shan,

22:16.480 --> 22:20.160
Houzi, Mei Hao, A-shuang, and K.O.

22:20.240 --> 22:21.720
will attend the Shanghai demo.

22:22.120 --> 22:24.760
The rest of you are now
on a two-week vacation.

22:25.560 --> 22:26.880
Two weeks?

22:26.960 --> 22:27.800
Paid?

22:28.360 --> 22:29.200
Of course.

22:34.760 --> 22:36.400
Thanks for your hard work.

22:36.480 --> 22:37.720
Go home and rest.

22:38.120 --> 22:39.640
As for tomorrow's demo,

22:39.960 --> 22:43.200
you can bring up any suggestions
or ideas right now.

22:44.840 --> 22:45.720
I have a suggestion.

22:46.320 --> 22:49.880
As an artist,
I take no issue with everything else,

22:49.960 --> 22:51.160
except for these guys here.

22:51.520 --> 22:54.360
You'll be representing Zhiyi Tech.

22:54.720 --> 22:57.280
Can you maybe clean up your looks a bit?

22:57.720 --> 23:00.240
Not you, Mr. Xiao, of course.

23:00.480 --> 23:01.880
Your face is attractive enough.

23:03.160 --> 23:04.840
As for the others,

23:04.920 --> 23:07.720
I think they would benefit
from some shopping

23:08.080 --> 23:09.440
and grooming.

23:09.680 --> 23:12.960
Take Yugong, for example, not neat at all.

23:16.640 --> 23:18.720
You think I'm not neat? Huh?

23:18.920 --> 23:22.200
It's not that you're not neat,
you just don't look tidy.

23:24.120 --> 23:27.560
This is a good suggestion.
I think we should take it.

23:28.160 --> 23:29.320
Any other issues?

23:29.680 --> 23:30.880
No.

23:31.960 --> 23:32.800
You're dismissed.

23:41.200 --> 23:42.280
I'll skip Shanghai.

23:43.280 --> 23:44.960
I don't like social events.

23:45.760 --> 23:48.480
Plus, I don't like formal wear.

23:51.320 --> 23:54.320
You can skip the demo,
since you don't like to talk,

23:54.400 --> 23:58.280
but you should let us see you
in formal wear.

23:59.240 --> 24:04.520
Boss, I have a suit.
I'll take a rain check.

24:04.920 --> 24:07.280
I want to go home and rest.
I don't feel well.

24:09.280 --> 24:11.320
Okay, see you at the airport.

24:17.760 --> 24:20.520
Why is A-shuang acting so weird?

24:21.280 --> 24:23.280
He's clearly overworked.

24:23.560 --> 24:26.400
I feel a bit weird myself.

24:26.640 --> 24:29.640
Let's have a meeting and discuss
the details of the demo.

24:31.880 --> 24:34.560
Fine, we'll do it in the morning.

24:35.680 --> 24:36.920
Perk up!

24:37.280 --> 24:39.360
Let's go optimize your looks.

24:43.160 --> 24:47.280
- Come with us, Wei-wei.
- Okay.

24:54.560 --> 24:57.200
Lady, bring me your best-looking suits.

24:57.280 --> 24:59.040
If there's only one, give it to me.

24:59.120 --> 25:00.080
- No, me!
- Me, too.

25:00.160 --> 25:01.520
Should we shop elsewhere?

25:02.920 --> 25:05.680
Please find a suit for this guy, too.

25:05.760 --> 25:06.680
Sure.

25:21.360 --> 25:22.600
Won't you pick one?

25:23.040 --> 25:25.840
I have several formal suits.
I don't need anything.

25:40.440 --> 25:42.960
You shouldn't wear the same suit as me.

25:43.040 --> 25:45.440
You'll only expose your flaws.

25:46.600 --> 25:50.320
You're worried my buff figure
would make you look like a sissy.

25:50.840 --> 25:54.280
Stop bickering, you two. This suit...

25:54.360 --> 25:57.800
is perfect for a mature and solid man
like me.

25:58.720 --> 25:59.840
You should wear something else.

26:03.200 --> 26:07.280
Mrs. Nai, you be the judge.
Who looks the best?

26:13.600 --> 26:15.200
Why do you guys insist on the same suit?

26:16.240 --> 26:18.200
Only by wearing the same suit,

26:18.280 --> 26:21.280
can you tell
who has the most attractive face.

26:28.600 --> 26:30.200
You all look handsome,

26:30.840 --> 26:33.720
but it's better not to wear the same suit.

26:33.800 --> 26:35.440
People would think you bought wholesale.

26:36.080 --> 26:37.720
How can we all look handsome?

26:37.800 --> 26:41.800
There's got to be a number one,
two, and three.

26:41.960 --> 26:46.080
Mrs. Nai, can't you pay attention
to elegance?

26:49.920 --> 26:51.360
Ms. Wei-wei, be sincere.

26:51.560 --> 26:54.440
Is it so hard for you to tell the truth?

26:56.360 --> 26:59.760
Tell the truth?
Let me organize my thoughts.

27:13.440 --> 27:15.520
Mr. K.O. is so handsome!

27:25.360 --> 27:27.640
Why are you looking at me?

27:30.040 --> 27:31.320
I don't feel right.

27:33.160 --> 27:35.480
You didn't fix the collar.

27:36.120 --> 27:39.760
Seriously, how can you look so handsome
when the suit's messy?

27:41.000 --> 27:44.160
Nobody fastens the second button.
What a bumpkin!

27:46.520 --> 27:47.680
I don't know these things.

27:48.520 --> 27:51.880
It's okay, you don't have to know.
You're handsome.

27:53.400 --> 27:54.360
Never mind.

27:54.440 --> 27:56.640
I'll pick something livelier,

27:56.720 --> 27:57.920
something more me.

27:59.800 --> 28:04.480
Fine, I'll go find... something darker.

28:05.560 --> 28:08.440
Help me look for a suit.

28:17.360 --> 28:20.600
I had no idea Mr. K.O.
would look so handsome in a suit.

28:23.560 --> 28:24.760
Why are you looking at me?

28:26.320 --> 28:28.600
I'm comparing you
to the first time you saw me.

28:37.480 --> 28:41.480
- I'll try this one in my size. Thanks.
- Sure.

28:42.000 --> 28:44.920
- You're buying a suit?
- Just trying it on.

28:55.920 --> 28:58.080
Hello? Er-xi, get a cab
and come over now.

28:58.160 --> 29:01.240
Come watch hot guys try on suits.
Miss this, you'll regret it forever.

29:01.640 --> 29:04.320
What? For real? What hot guys?

29:05.080 --> 29:05.920
From Lord's office.

29:08.360 --> 29:13.120
Hot guys in suits? I'm coming right now.

29:13.280 --> 29:14.360
Why are you being so nice?

29:14.440 --> 29:16.720
You know to share a sweet deal with me!

29:18.720 --> 29:21.320
I just hate to look like a fangirl.

29:21.400 --> 29:26.080
So I want you to be here
to express my feelings through your face.

29:42.520 --> 29:44.600
Hey. What's the address?

29:44.920 --> 29:46.920
You can stay home now.

29:47.000 --> 29:50.360
What? Why? I'm ready to head out.

29:50.960 --> 29:52.680
Because I want this for myself.

29:57.120 --> 29:59.600
Stinky Wei-wei! You put beaus before BFFs!

30:07.920 --> 30:10.440
ZHIYI TECH

30:17.480 --> 30:19.240
I told you, you can't win.

30:19.400 --> 30:21.080
Nai Xiao finished optimization in time.

30:21.240 --> 30:24.640
Looks like he is indeed
a powerful competitor.

30:24.840 --> 30:26.600
Thankfully, I'm well-prepared.

30:27.120 --> 30:30.240
You're not needed
for the rest of the plan. Just take care.

30:31.080 --> 30:32.800
The best is yet to come.

30:44.240 --> 30:46.400
Thank you for shopping with us.

30:49.920 --> 30:50.960
I'll take Wei-wei back.

30:51.040 --> 30:54.320
- Okay. See you at the airport. Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

30:54.400 --> 30:55.240
- Bye-bye.
- See you.

30:56.720 --> 30:58.840
- Let's head back to your place.
- Okay.

30:59.000 --> 31:00.480
I'll pack and go to the airport.

31:01.080 --> 31:03.120
Good. I'm leaving tomorrow, too.

31:03.440 --> 31:04.440
To your roommate's place?

31:05.920 --> 31:08.120
Have you been so busy,
you forgot the date?

31:08.200 --> 31:10.800
School starts tomorrow.
I'm moving back to campus.

31:13.680 --> 31:14.520
Let's go.

31:27.320 --> 31:30.960
MONDAY, AUGUST 31st, 2015

31:42.760 --> 31:44.720
I can't take you
to get registered tomorrow.

31:45.960 --> 31:47.960
It'd be scary, if you do.

31:48.040 --> 31:50.120
A crowd might gather around us.

32:08.160 --> 32:09.240
Who can it be?

32:17.640 --> 32:18.640
Dad!

32:18.720 --> 32:19.920
Where are my Bei-hong Xus?

32:20.520 --> 32:24.320
Where did you put my Bei-hong Xus
and Guan-zhong Wus?

32:24.400 --> 32:26.360
- You...
- What's the hurry? Your paintings

32:26.440 --> 32:28.280
can't run off anywhere.

32:33.240 --> 32:34.560
Why are you two standing here?

32:35.280 --> 32:36.880
Wei-wei, go make tea.

32:48.160 --> 32:49.200
Here are the paintings.

32:49.880 --> 32:51.600
I was so worried.

32:53.520 --> 32:54.760
Easy.

32:54.840 --> 32:57.080
- Manuscripts.
- Set them aside.

33:01.000 --> 33:03.880
Why are you thinking about
the paintings now?

33:04.160 --> 33:06.440
Are they more important
than your daughter-in-law?

33:13.240 --> 33:15.720
Nai Xiao, as your parents,

33:15.800 --> 33:18.480
we're not close-minded,
but your girlfriend

33:18.560 --> 33:20.040
- hasn't graduated--
- It's not what you think.

33:20.720 --> 33:23.800
There's an issue with her accommodation.
So she stayed here for a few days.

33:25.600 --> 33:26.440
What about you?

33:26.920 --> 33:30.200
I've been staying at the office.
I just got back.

33:30.280 --> 33:31.960
I'm flying to Shanghai tonight,

33:32.280 --> 33:34.080
for a demo at Fengteng Technology.

33:34.760 --> 33:37.800
Wei-wei is moving back to the dorm.
That's why she's packing.

33:44.160 --> 33:46.800
We're not close-minded parents,
it's just...

33:48.800 --> 33:51.160
Do you support them or not?

33:52.000 --> 33:53.840
Mind your paintings and stay out of this.

33:53.920 --> 33:57.880
Look. You wanted me to care,
and now you don't.

33:57.960 --> 34:00.200
Can you tell me what you want?

34:01.360 --> 34:04.480
Come to a consensus, you two.
I'll be in the kitchen.

34:07.840 --> 34:08.679
You...

34:12.840 --> 34:14.040
What now?

34:15.040 --> 34:16.360
Do Professor Xiao

34:16.440 --> 34:19.239
and Professor Lin think
I'm a girl with loose morals?

34:20.159 --> 34:22.280
They tend to think
I'm the one with loose morals.

34:24.239 --> 34:25.679
But just in case,

34:26.320 --> 34:28.080
you can act like a victim.

34:29.400 --> 34:30.840
I'd like to,

34:30.920 --> 34:33.360
but I've been eating with you guys,

34:33.440 --> 34:34.639
and I've put on weight.

34:34.719 --> 34:36.679
No victim is so well-fed and robust.

34:37.600 --> 34:38.920
Meaning?

34:39.639 --> 34:43.440
You'd really play the victim,
if you didn't put on weight?

34:44.440 --> 34:46.440
It's a must, meeting mother...

34:48.520 --> 34:50.280
When meeting others,
the first impression is key.

34:51.040 --> 34:53.840
Don't worry. I've explained everything.

34:54.400 --> 34:55.800
Go serve your mother-in-law tea.

35:01.000 --> 35:01.840
Go, now.

35:03.160 --> 35:04.240
Fine.

35:15.240 --> 35:17.680
Professor Lin, Professor Xiao,
have some tea.

35:18.200 --> 35:20.440
- Sit down.
- Sit.

35:27.760 --> 35:29.600
Your paper is well written.

35:31.280 --> 35:32.640
Thanks, Professor.

35:34.880 --> 35:38.920
There was an issue
with my roommate's accommodation,

35:39.120 --> 35:40.960
so I stayed here for a few days.

35:42.320 --> 35:44.720
Nai Xiao already told us. It's okay.

35:45.040 --> 35:47.160
Your department chair
lives next door to us.

35:47.240 --> 35:51.120
He's sang your praises.
We know you're a good girl.

35:51.200 --> 35:54.480
We're not close-minded parents, if...

35:56.200 --> 35:57.400
I should go to the airport.

35:57.840 --> 36:01.040
Mom, Wei-wei is going back to campus.
I can't take her.

36:01.120 --> 36:03.520
Give her a ride,
when you go back to campus.

36:04.000 --> 36:05.240
Sure.

36:06.680 --> 36:08.800
Don't... Um...

36:08.880 --> 36:11.200
I don't want to trouble you, really.

36:11.280 --> 36:12.200
It's fine.

36:22.480 --> 36:24.720
Uncle and Auntie, my dorm is up there.

36:24.800 --> 36:26.160
- You don't have to walk me.
- It's fine.

36:26.240 --> 36:28.800
We'll walk you to the door.
It's just ahead?

36:29.640 --> 36:31.840
Isn't that archaeology's Professor Xiao?

36:31.920 --> 36:34.320
Yes, the other is our department's
Professor Lin.

36:35.400 --> 36:38.760
What? Wei-wei Bei has met
Nai Xiao's parents?

36:39.320 --> 36:41.480
Goodness! They're taking her to school?

36:41.560 --> 36:44.520
I've seen plenty of PTAs, but never seen
anyone show off parents-in-law.

36:44.600 --> 36:47.920
- What a sickening scheme!
- Right?

36:52.000 --> 36:53.600
- Is this it?
- Yes.

36:53.800 --> 36:55.080
- Here.
- It's heavy.

36:55.320 --> 36:56.240
It's okay.

36:56.320 --> 36:58.360
All right. Thank you so much, Uncle.

36:58.440 --> 37:00.960
I'll ask my roommates to help me.

37:01.040 --> 37:02.960
- Are you sure? That's a lot of stuff.
- We'll be fine.

37:03.160 --> 37:06.240
Don't be a stranger.
Come visit often, when Nai Xiao returns.

37:06.320 --> 37:07.440
- Okay.
- Good.

37:07.840 --> 37:09.000
I'll take this.

37:09.080 --> 37:11.120
I'll walk you out, Auntie and Uncle.

37:11.200 --> 37:12.800
- It's fine.
- It's okay.

37:12.880 --> 37:15.440
- We'll see ourselves out.
- Head upstairs.

37:15.560 --> 37:17.080
- All right.
- Be careful.

37:17.160 --> 37:18.960
- Goodbye.
- Bye, Uncle and Auntie.

37:25.480 --> 37:27.840
We heard the gossip from upstairs!
Where are his parents?

37:27.920 --> 37:30.160
Lord's parents dropped you off?

37:30.600 --> 37:32.960
You're amazing, Wei-wei!

37:33.160 --> 37:36.400
Other people get dropped off by parents.
You got dropped off by parents-in-law?

37:37.560 --> 37:38.400
Carry my things.

37:39.160 --> 37:40.560
We want details!

37:40.640 --> 37:42.480
- Come on!
- Details!

37:50.680 --> 37:52.920
Hello? Have you landed?

37:54.480 --> 37:56.680
That's fast. The flight wasn't delayed?

37:58.680 --> 38:00.440
Traffic's bad in Shanghai, too?

38:02.840 --> 38:06.120
Okay, don't let me keep you.
Get some rest.

38:07.520 --> 38:08.360
Bye-bye.

38:11.200 --> 38:12.320
"Get some rest."

38:12.600 --> 38:13.680
"Okay, bye-bye."

38:14.400 --> 38:16.480
So sweet!

38:17.280 --> 38:19.160
You and Da-zhong have been like that
for two years.

38:19.240 --> 38:20.960
Don't I get to counterattack?

38:22.200 --> 38:25.800
Enough, you two.
Er-xi and I have it worse.

38:30.800 --> 38:33.280
Didn't you just brush your teeth?
Did you forget?

38:35.320 --> 38:38.320
I snuck some food,
after I brushed my teeth.

38:40.120 --> 38:41.200
What did she say?

38:41.920 --> 38:44.240
She said she snuck some food
after she brushed her teeth.

38:46.840 --> 38:49.680
The big snack pack you brought back.

38:50.440 --> 38:51.680
Huh? What?

38:52.680 --> 38:54.960
The big snack pack you brought back.

38:56.640 --> 38:57.480
Amazing.

39:19.600 --> 39:23.560
After a long day,
I finally get to pamper myself.

39:24.800 --> 39:28.320
Wait, when did the two of you make up?

39:28.400 --> 39:30.280
Why did you fight? Tell us!

39:33.240 --> 39:38.600
Why we fought doesn't matter.
The question is,

39:38.680 --> 39:40.920
where did someone move to
after our fight?

39:41.440 --> 39:44.440
- Right!
- What happened, Wei-wei?

39:44.520 --> 39:45.360
What's going on?

39:46.040 --> 39:47.920
- Tell us! What happened?
- Nothing!

39:48.200 --> 39:49.640
- Nothing!
- Tell us!

39:49.720 --> 39:51.480
Nothing, I swear.

39:51.560 --> 39:54.080
What do you want? Nothing happened!

39:57.840 --> 39:59.920
FIRST SEMESTER, SEPTEMBER 2015
REGISTERED

40:03.000 --> 40:05.840
STAMPING

40:09.680 --> 40:13.000
Amazing, Xiao-ling.
You shop while standing in line.

40:13.080 --> 40:15.240
What do you know? I'm being efficient.

40:15.320 --> 40:17.880
There's a huge sale today.
It's a great deal.

40:17.960 --> 40:19.400
I've waited for this forever.

40:19.640 --> 40:21.840
Look, this brand is 70 percent off.

40:22.360 --> 40:25.840
Let me see! It's true!
I have to snatch up a bargain.

40:25.920 --> 40:29.120
Right? A new look for the new semester.

40:29.200 --> 40:31.120
Let them see us gloriously transformed.

40:31.200 --> 40:32.920
Make them jealous.

40:33.800 --> 40:35.800
We're almost up. Shop later.

40:35.880 --> 40:37.040
Hold on.

40:38.680 --> 40:40.520
Okay, I finished in time.

40:42.440 --> 40:44.440
The cart is only good for 20 minutes.

40:44.520 --> 40:47.440
If you don't pay in time,
you'll lose the deal.

40:47.680 --> 40:49.920
It takes money to be a fast payer.

40:56.280 --> 40:57.880
We're juniors already!

40:57.960 --> 41:00.480
I still remember
our military training class.

41:00.560 --> 41:04.080
Like when you got reprimanded
for faking a stomachache?

41:04.160 --> 41:05.120
You're always...

41:05.200 --> 41:07.320
Enough, you two.

41:07.800 --> 41:09.440
What are your plans for later?

41:09.520 --> 41:11.760
I'm getting my intern pay
from Zhenyi Tech.

41:11.840 --> 41:13.400
Who's going with me?

41:14.360 --> 41:16.400
I made plans with Da-zhong.

41:16.480 --> 41:19.160
It's... that time of the month for me.

41:19.240 --> 41:20.480
You have no love.

41:20.560 --> 41:22.600
Even if I do, you won't get it.

41:22.680 --> 41:24.840
- I'm taking off. Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

41:26.480 --> 41:27.560
Wei-wei?

41:27.640 --> 41:29.680
Fine, I'm free anyway.

41:30.800 --> 41:31.640
Let's go.

41:31.720 --> 41:34.840
Wait here. Nature calls. Be right back!

41:35.360 --> 41:36.440
Hurry!

41:37.040 --> 41:39.320
MEN'S ROOM

44:18.880 --> 44:21.320
Subtitle translation by Yu-han Lu
